      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施依赖的流程图，核心组件是Redis缓存层，它下面要挂Etcd集群做配置中心，最外层再用Ingress Controller统一入口流量。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个基础设施组件。我想确认一下流向：Redis在最上游，Etcd在中间承接，Ingress Controller在下游接收？还是Ingress作为入口在最前面？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Ingress Controller确实在最下游，流量从Redis经过Etcd再到Ingress。不过这里不是严格的调用链，而是部署层面的依赖关系——Redis和Etcd要先就绪，Ingress才能正常启动。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把三个节点按TB方向竖排：Redis在顶部，Etcd居中，Ingress Controller在底部，用实线连接表示启动依赖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "方向对了，但线条样式我需要再想想——目前用实线可以，不过最好标注这是启动依赖而非数据流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "要不我先保持简洁的无标签实线？TB布局本身已经暗示了层级，太多文字反而杂乱。如果后续需要区分数据流和依赖流，我们再补标签。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，先这样。三个节点命名也统一用Infra_前缀，方便和其他业务图区分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下最终结构：TB方向，Infra_RedisCache指向Infra_EtcdCluster，再指向Infra_IngressController，无标签实线连接。这样是否符合预期？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
